rows.label: tlk42350162_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh-meh!
Esasa thought would never make
it back alive!

rows.label: tlk42350162_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Esasa was on way to Iyasaki on
business errand...

rows.label: tlk42350162_01_msg0003
rows.name:
When all of sudden, Esasa lose footing
on narrow road and slip into Cloud Sea!

rows.label: tlk42350162_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Esasa manage to Noppy-paddle to
safety on small island, but was great
struggle to reach surface again...

rows.label: tlk42350162_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Friends have bigger bodies than Esasa,
so should watch steps even closer!
